2ï¸âƒ£ UML Sequence Diagram â€“ Invocation Submission

Now hereâ€™s the interaction model.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Maker
    participant System as BC & OR Portal
    participant DB as Database
    actor Checker

    Maker->>System: Click Invocation
    System-->>Maker: Display Invocation Form

    Maker->>System: Enter Disruption Details
    System->>System: Validate Mandatory Fields

    alt Validation Failed
        System-->>Maker: Show Error Messages
    else Validation Success
        System->>DB: Save Invocation Data
        DB-->>System: Data Stored
    end

    Maker->>System: Select Resilience Level
    Maker->>System: Click Validate & Submit

    System->>System: Final Validation

    alt Final Validation Failed
        System-->>Maker: Return with Errors
    else Final Validation Passed
        System->>DB: Update Status = SUBMITTED
        System->>Checker: Notify for Review
        System-->>Maker: Submission Successful
    end


